# Grok Math Review

For mathematical, statistical, benchmark, scoring, evaluation, or experimental-validity tasks in this project, ask a Grok subagent for an independent opinion before finalizing the change.

Use the Grok review to look for metric leakage, biased scoring, invalid aggregation, weak baselines, hidden assumptions, and failure cases. Treat the review as advice, not authority.
